
                             Angular 6


Backend :-

1)Create project folder:--- ex: nikhilagro

2)Inside the nikhilagro create package.json file:-   $ npm init

3)then install express :- $ sudo npm install express  - - save

4)create server.js file.

5)install cors :- $ sudo npm install cors

6)install body-Parser:- $ sudo npm install --save body-parser

Frontend :-

1) install angular :-  $ sudo npm install -g @angular/cli

2)create frontend directory angular new project frontend :- $ sudo ng new frontend

3) go inside frontend and open your project :- $ sudo ng new frontend

